{"tid":1436802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【戰術文】陣地戰贏，輿論戰也要贏","createTime":"2019-08-09T11:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:13:51.000Z","uid":28942,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"229608ae70aa2d758280251b6955b719787ea959","tid":1436802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:06:17.000Z","msg":"打得好辛苦，麻煩幫忙推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明眼人最近當然看得出林鄭政府在打的就是輿論戰， 包括跨部門新聞發布會，每日警犬記者招待會和間中的特首見記者。目的只有一個，帶動輿論。<br />\n<br />\n假設我們現在什麼都不做，任由政府帶動輿論，最終效果有以下：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>1. 政府成功分化和理非和勇武，經濟派和民主自由派，上一代和下一代</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>2. 整個風波會變成&lsquo;一小撮極端暴力分子&rsquo;的責任，政府無需問責</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>3. 警察成為最終&lsquo;受害者&rsquo;，同情警察忘記受到警暴的義士</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>4. 香港最終成為政治冷感的地方</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n從政府最近的言論來看，政府所用的戰術其實不是新的東西。著名社會學家Frank Furedi 就已經講過不同政客或者商家會用&lsquo;Fear&rsquo; 恐懼 和&rsquo;Risk&rsquo; 危機 來帶動輿論。原因是恐懼是最能牽動人們的情緒。例子有最近的鐳射槍和經濟民生論，甚至送中條例本身都帶來了很大的恐懼，所以號召力非常厲害。<br />\n那麼我們有什麼可以做去抗衡政府現在的策略？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 不但要攻擊政府黑警，也要攻擊他們的&lsquo;記者會&rsquo;</span></strong></span><br />\n要從源頭入手，discredit 他們的記者會。指出他們真正的詭計是要控制輿論危言聳聽而不是所謂的溝通。讓市民不要信服他們散播的恐懼<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 要用sound bite 來對抗恐懼,而且要不斷重複</span></span></strong><br />\n對於有獨立思考的年輕人來說，要破解政府的危言聳聽當然簡單。但是對於一般普羅大眾來說，要自己Fact Check是困難的，他們也懶得去慢慢聽家中年輕一輩的解說。所以簡易的sound bite 是必須的<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 以其人之道還治其人之身</span></span></strong><br />\n既然警犬和政府不願面對事實，面對自己的錯失。為求達到自己的政治目的寧可要全港市民人心惶惶 。我們一樣可以！重點應該放在一些影響公眾安全的東西，例如過期催淚煙，警黑合作等等。目標是要人民害怕的不是示威者，不是勇武，而是政府本身!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4. 不墮落圈套，Be Humble</span></span></strong><br />\n共產黨當年也是一樣，對農民非常禮貌。我們也要一樣！如果我們再不斷攻擊無辜市民，我們就會跌入了政府的陷阱。 Be Water and Be Humble.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5. 行動繼續，繼續核彈都唔割！</span></span></strong><br />\n好像元朗事件後，所有人都找到最大公約數，就是對黑社會的厭惡和對警犬無能的控訴。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><em><ins>兄弟爬山，香港人有的是創意！陣地戰贏，輿論戰也要贏！</ins></em></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港人，加油！</div></span></span></em></strong>"},{"pid":"d37b9ff899c077803ad734827515d3f64afce096","tid":1436802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:07:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2d9a1a7593854ee8a5ccd7178223740c69cb2b2","tid":1436802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:08:00.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"39b9d991a7e5213451a9af83daf36cf9e738cc20","tid":1436802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:08:29.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"66ff5ed98a958046f09150ef67d8076e29db092d","tid":1436802,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef949f4beb58f8f2d92ba82e83721caafe8089d","tid":1436802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:08:51.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"5359108bc2a81b16f7a29e90eca78c082b11a9ad","tid":1436802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:09:22.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"534fc9aa4336533237a0c905af8e63ea9761fa78","tid":1436802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:17.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"65e74cf2c942d874ab6e8e1e9a8c798fe5d295e5","tid":1436802,"uid":4050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解一定係佢地開主題我地曬時間去駁佢？ 點解唔係我地開主題佢地之後回應我地</strong>？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想知<span style=\"color: green;\">鐳射筆，外國勢力，大台，經濟差</span><br />\n<br />\n想知<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>葉虎，同志們，過期彈呀</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f2f3993ee90298f4d97abdc141cf5e4193700e52","tid":1436802,"uid":270398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:48.000Z","msg":"要佔番上風既話其實要主動出擊, 唔可以次次等仍開記者會分化我地再諗點拆"},{"pid":"fdc046dcdd58bf8b74119a8fdf45c9fc61af8390","tid":1436802,"uid":146520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:54.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"62d3dc8ae2d60547be7d31b7692da3fcea71a00b","tid":1436802,"uid":28942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2f3993ee90298f4d97abdc141cf5e4193700e52","tid":1436802,"uid":270398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:48.000Z","msg":"要佔番上風既話其實要主動出擊, 唔可以次次等仍開記者會分化我地再諗點拆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:11:25.000Z","msg":"同意！"},{"pid":"735e6215a247f857c65edbbe0c8ba082abbfaadf","tid":1436802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"要帶動輿論嘅應該係我地！"},{"pid":"dfc22098e4ee5e84642e8933c5898094d77a87a4","tid":1436802,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6abb643b9f2bcd9c058efb4eea1796149915c1ee","tid":1436802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c65e9da5cc7da7081a83c17c81f5a268ad3a09","tid":1436802,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:13:50.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e42f8842ff8077fe2019d7abb477ad811214f2b","tid":1436802,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:14:30.000Z","msg":"佢真係好垃圾"},{"pid":"e7a8de043562718717ff8ae286c8708a6b59f61e","tid":1436802,"uid":294052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"唔打陣地戰呀 打游擊戰呀 令警犬疲於奔命 弱其意志 滅其精神<br />\n將抗爭帶落區 令一般市民感同身受 連結反政府思想<br />\n文宣！ 傳單！ 文映會！"},{"pid":"c64d5aade923d7d7f9b38eaf475b02102e265741","tid":1436802,"uid":261223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd178ff0d811c48787020b93ad9b76abc95038db","tid":1436802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:22:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f590fd30a37b11164c87f7ac82a2d953b7bd51c7","tid":1436802,"uid":300846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65e74cf2c942d874ab6e8e1e9a8c798fe5d295e5","tid":1436802,"uid":4050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解一定係佢地開主題我地曬時間去駁佢？ 點解唔係我地開主題佢地之後回應我地</strong>？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想知<span style=\"color: green;\">鐳射筆，外國勢力，大台，經濟差</span><br />\n<br />\n想知<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>葉虎，同志們，過期彈呀</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:53:20.000Z","msg":"過期催淚彈，仲有警黑勾結<br />\n<br />\n警方而家收到福建幫的斬人預告未？警方知唔知發出斬人預告係犯法？<br />\n<br />\n警方打算在被預告當日如何部署？係咪安排所有警員遠離黑社會？如果見到有人斬人係咪一個都唔拘捕？點解元朗警察一消失就即刻有人出來打人？點解防暴警察同拎住木棍的暴徒會搭膊頭？<br />\n<br />\n涉事警察有無受到處分？如果無，係咩原因？（通常話係當值人數太多無法確定是哪一個）<br />\n如果你地無法確定，咁點解仲可以唔帶委任值然後同市民講話「只要有一個人有委任證就得，有相就會知道係邊個」？<br />\n<br />\n一定要引爆佢地自相矛盾的立論"},{"pid":"20b2219fd249ac8420dd9bd29efcce47be0c692b","tid":1436802,"uid":281418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b81fc009ec3e5fec28542192673808d41774291b","tid":1436802,"uid":245602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07BvS0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07BvS0w.jpg&h=942acfd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19fef2254a2cf7000c76de203c465c980b0b7ccf","tid":1436802,"uid":278797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:13:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}